'''矢状腹径'''（'''SAD'''）是一種量測腹部[[脂肪組織|脂肪組織]]的方式，是背部到上腹部之間的厚度。矢状腹径可以在站立時量測<ref name=pmid17041127>{{cite journal |first1=Carlos |last1=Iribarren |first2=Jeanne A. |last2=Darbinian |first3=Joan C. |last3=Lo |first4=Bruce H. |last4=Fireman |first5=Alan S. |last5=Go |year=2006 |title=Value of the Sagittal Abdominal Diameter in Coronary Heart Disease Risk Assessment: Cohort Study in a Large, Multiethnic Population |journal=American Journal of Epidemiology |volume=164 |issue=12 |pages=1150–9 |doi=10.1093/aje/kwj341 |pmid=17041127}}</ref>，也可以在仰臥時量測<ref name=pmid17391519>{{cite journal |first1=Helena |last1=Petersson |first2=Achraf |last2=Daryani |first3=Ulf |last3=Risérus |year=2007 |title=Sagittal abdominal diameter as a marker of inflammation and insulin resistance among immigrant women from the Middle East and native Swedish women: a cross-sectional study |journal=Cardiovascular Diabetology |volume=6 |pages=10 |pmid=17391519 |pmc=1847804 |doi=10.1186/1475-2840-6-10}}</ref>。矢状腹径可以由任何一點量測，從最后肋骨和髂嵴之間的最窄處，到髂嵴的中點皆可<ref name=pmid17041127 /><ref name=pmid17391519 /><ref name=doi10.1111/j.1365-277X.2012.01267.x>{{cite journal |first1=HA |last1=de Almeida Paula |first2=R |last2=de Cássia Lanes Ribeiro |first3=LEFP |last3=de Lima Rosado |first4=MV |last4=Abranches |first5=S |last5=do Carmo Castro Franceschini |date=31 July 2012 |title=Relationship between waist circumference and supine abdominal height measured at different anatomical sites and cardiometabolic risk factors in older women |journal=Journal of Human Nutrition and Dietetics |volume=25 |issue=6 |pages=563–8 |doi=10.1111/j.1365-277X.2012.01267.x |pmid=23173640 |url=http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1365-277X.2012.01267.x/abstract |access-date=2015-10-26 |archive-date=2015-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151203141843/http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1365-277X.2012.01267.x/abstract |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

矢状腹径可以有效預測[[冠狀動脈疾病|冠狀動脈疾病]]，其數值越高，其風險越高，此風險和[[身高體重指數|身高體重指數]]無關<ref name=pmid17041127 />。

對於有正常[[身高體重指數|身高體重指數]]的人，其矢状腹径需小於{{convert|25|cm|in}}。矢状腹径和{{convert|30|cm|in}}相減的數值和[[心血管疾病|心血管疾病]]及[[胰島素抵抗|胰島素抵抗]]有正相關<ref name=pmid17391519 />。男性在四十歲時，若矢状腹径大於25 cm，其在三十年後罹患[[阿兹海默病|阿兹海默病]]的比例也顯著提高<ref>{{cite journal |pages=1057–64 |doi=10.1212/01.wnl.0000306313.89165.ef |title=Central obesity and increased risk of dementia more than three decades later |year=2008 |last1=Whitmer |first1=R. A. |last2=Gustafson |first2=D. R. |last3=Barrett-Connor |first3=E. |last4=Haan |first4=M. N. |last5=Gunderson |first5=E. P. |last6=Yaffe |first6=K. |journal=Neurology |volume=71 |issue=14 |pmid=18367704}}</ref>。一篇{{le|神经病学年鉴|Annals of Neurology}}的論文也將腹部脂肪連結到較小的大腦容量<ref>{{cite journal |pages=136–44 |doi=10.1002/ana.22062 |title=Visceral fat is associated with lower brain volume in healthy middle-aged adults |year=2010 |last1=Debette |first1=Stéphanie |last2=Beiser |first2=Alexa |last3=Hoffmann |first3=Udo |last4=Decarli |first4=Charles |last5=O'Donnell |first5=Christopher J. |last6=Massaro |first6=Joseph M. |last7=Au |first7=Rhoda |last8=Himali |first8=Jayandra J. |last9=Wolf |first9=Philip A. |last10=Fox |first10=Caroline S. |last11=Seshadri |first11=Sudha |journal=Annals of Neurology}}</ref>。

另一個相關的量測是{{le|仰臥腹部高度|Supine Abdominal Height}}（SAH），是在{{le|仰臥|supine position}}時腹部的高度<ref>{{cite journal |pages=2041–6 |doi=10.2337/diacare.27.8.2041 |title=Sagittal Abdominal Diameter Is a Strong Anthropometric Marker of Insulin Resistance and Hyperproinsulinemia in Obese Men |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_diabetes-care_2004-08_27_8/page/2041 |year=2004 |last1=Riserus |first1=Ulf |last2=Ärnlöv |first2=Johan |last3=Brismar |first3=Kerstin |last4=Zethelius |first4=Björn |last5=Berglund |first5=Lars |last6=Vessby |first6=Bengt |journal=Diabetes Care |volume=27 |issue=8 |pmid=15277437}}</ref>。SAH法較容易自我監控，但因為重力的關係，其數值會比較小，數值不能直接和矢状腹径比較{{Citation needed|date=2015-10}}。

